title: The 'Boys & Girl with Jane Slater - Dominant Philly W; Player Reaction; Cowboys' Midseason Identity; Garrett Job Security; Dak Contract
itunes:title: The 'Boys & Girl with Jane Slater - Dominant Philly W; Player Reaction; Cowboys' Midseason Identity; Garrett Job Security; Dak Contract
description:
On the premiere episode of all-Cowboys 'Boys and Girl Podcast, NFL Network Reporter Jane Slater and producer/co-host Bobby Belt discuss Dallas' identity at the midway point after a dominant divisional win over Philadelphia. Follow Jane and Bobby on Twitter and subscribe to get all the latest inside information from two of the most connected people in the Cowboys' community.
